data.description: Welcome to 422 Tibbetts St. located in the Harvest at Limoneira community. Exceptional opportunity to purchase a highly desirable Vinelands floorplan and End unit. Possible assumption of Sellers VA loan at VERY low rate by VA qualified buyers. Built in 2019 this pristine home offers 1,880sf of living space including 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms! The first floor offers an open concept layout with one full bedroom with bath, dining area and large great room that seamlessly flows into kitchen. High ceilings offer plenty of ambient light and there is ample space for the entire family to gather and entertain. The gourmet kitchen features GE Profile stainless steel appliances, Granite countertops with updated backsplash and a large sit-down center island. Sellers have upgraded the wood floors and window treatments throughout when originally purchased from Lennar. Head upstairs and you will find the second bedroom with it's own full bathroom. Continue on to the spacious loft which gives you even more versatile living space. Loft could be converted to a 4th bedroom. Master bedroom offers plenty of room for a large bed with room to spare. The Master Suite bathroom offers his and hers separate sinks, shower, soaking tub along with a spacious walk-in closet. Make you way out to the landscaped backyard patio with upgraded pavers and low maintenance synthetic turf. Turf continues down side of house, perfect for a dog run. This smart home features recessed (dimmable) LED lights throughout, fully pre-wired Ethernet and Wi-Fi boosters and Ring doorbell. In addition, the features will allow you to lock and unlock the front door, open and close the garage and control the air-conditioning all remotely from your phone, making this truly a smart home! Other notable features include a spacious garage with ample storage, tankless water heater and roof mounted solar panels. Residents also enjoy resort like living with access to the Farmhouse recreation area that includes a huge clubhouse, pool/spa, fitness gym, fire pit, BBQ and beautiful parks. Whether you work remotely from home or commute, this central location offers endless opportunities just 20 minutes to the beach and 30 min to I-5 freeway.
